271
00:21:27.537 --> 00:21:29.706
Yes, it's a play
on words. Yeah.

272
00:21:30.039 --> 00:21:31.040
Where?

273
00:21:37.881 --> 00:21:39.716
Looks about
half a mile out, sir.

274
00:21:40.758 --> 00:21:43.011
Do we wanna try
and swim it or...

275
00:21:43.136 --> 00:21:46.556
No, Bough. This is a job
for the shoebox inflatable.

276
00:21:46.681 --> 00:21:48.308
No, don't open it
in the car, sir!

277
00:21:54.814 --> 00:21:57.817
Can you reach
your door handle?

278
00:22:00.236 --> 00:22:01.821
No, sir.

279
00:22:02.322 --> 00:22:04.657
I'll try my side.

280
00:22:22.050 --> 00:22:26.054
Right, Bough, our aim is to get
on board without anyone noticing.

281
00:22:26.596 --> 00:22:28.264
And how are we gonna do it?

282
00:22:28.473 --> 00:22:30.850
Magnetic boots.
Brilliant, sir.

283
00:22:31.726 --> 00:22:33.144
Simple mechanism.

284
00:22:33.269 --> 00:22:36.397
Left switch activates left boot.
Right switch activates right.

285
00:22:37.106 --> 00:22:38.942
Okay, let's go.

286
00:22:53.831 --> 00:22:59.337
Remember, the absolutely vital
element of this mission is surprise.

287
00:23:21.025 --> 00:23:22.777
Now, you have to get up
pretty early in the morning

288
00:23:22.902 --> 00:23:25.029
to outwit
British Intelligence.

289
00:23:31.202 --> 00:23:32.287
Quick!

290
00:23:39.460 --> 00:23:41.296
Good evening, gentlemen.

291
00:23:42.589 --> 00:23:44.591
Shall we start
with your names?

292
00:23:45.717 --> 00:23:48.678
Clearly you have no idea
who you're dealing with.

293
00:23:49.679 --> 00:23:52.015
That's why I'm starting
with your names.

294
00:23:52.557 --> 00:23:54.434
Actually, would you mind
coming down here?

295
00:23:54.559 --> 00:23:57.228
It's really hard to have
a conversation like this.

296
00:23:58.605 --> 00:24:00.273
I have a better idea.

297
00:24:07.947 --> 00:24:09.657
It's no good,
it won't move, sir.

298
00:24:10.450 --> 00:24:12.368
We'll see about that.

299
00:24:12.493 --> 00:24:14.829
Low-intensity
exploding cotton bud.

300
00:24:18.666 --> 00:24:21.210
That's quite a powerful charge
for such a small space, sir.

301
00:24:21.294 --> 00:24:22.712
Oh, nonsense.

302
00:24:24.964 --> 00:24:27.133
There will just be
a slight pop.

303
00:24:35.141 --> 00:24:38.061
Shall we locate the hold
and look for the source of that signal?

304
00:24:38.144 --> 00:24:42.148
I think we should locate the hold
and look for the source of that signal!

305
00:24:45.485 --> 00:24:46.653
Come on!

306
00:24:58.539 --> 00:25:01.042
I'd say we have
our villain, Bough!

307
00:25:01.167 --> 00:25:03.336
You need to keep
your voice down, sir.

308
00:25:04.212 --> 00:25:06.214
And we're not going
to lose him.

309
00:25:19.727 --> 00:25:21.979
Hand me the sherbet fountain.

310
00:25:24.482 --> 00:25:27.485
Three sucks and the location
transmitter is activated.

311
00:25:27.568 --> 00:25:31.364
This gin palace will show up
