316
00:26:11.529 --> 00:26:13.364
Till we meet again.

317
00:26:21.497 --> 00:26:22.665
Ow!

318
00:26:27.253 --> 00:26:29.547
Well, that was sooner
than I expected.

319
00:26:33.384 --> 00:26:36.471
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow.

320
00:26:40.016 --> 00:26:41.893
<i>Who do you
think she is, sir?</i>

321
00:26:41.976 --> 00:26:44.645
Well, if she's not
the owner of that yacht,

322
00:26:44.729 --> 00:26:46.189
then she knows who is.

323
00:26:47.315 --> 00:26:49.817
Either way, she's the key
to this case.

324
00:26:52.153 --> 00:26:55.198
Is it true you were teaching,
sir? Before all this blew up?

325
00:26:56.491 --> 00:26:58.743
If by "teaching" you mean

326
00:26:58.868 --> 00:27:03.831
