operatives then yes, I was.

327
00:27:03.915 --> 00:27:04.999
Hmm.

328
00:27:05.082 --> 00:27:09.754
I actually got married, sir.
I don't know if you heard.

329
00:27:11.339 --> 00:27:12.340
No.

330
00:27:13.007 --> 00:27:14.342
Hmm.

331
00:27:14.550 --> 00:27:16.135
Yeah, Lydia.

332
00:27:16.219 --> 00:27:17.261
Lovely girl.

333
00:27:21.015 --> 00:27:23.684
You never think about getting
