owner of that yacht is.

498
00:43:33.028 --> 00:43:34.029
Jason Volta.

499
00:43:34.112 --> 00:43:36.323
The world's most powerful
Internet billionaire, sir!

500
00:43:36.406 --> 00:43:37.783
